                                    <h1 class="u-mb-m">Which of the following best describes your sexual orientation?</h1>
                                    
                                    <div class="u-mb-xs">
                                                {% from "components/details/_macro.njk" import onsDetails %}
                                                {{
                                                    onsDetails({
                                                        "id": "details",
                                                        "title": "Why we ask this question?",
                                                        "classes": "u-mb-m",
                                                        "content": "<p>We ask this question of people who are aged 16 years old and over.It’s up to you to decide how you answer this question. This question is voluntary, so you can leave it blank if you prefer.</p>",
