                                    <p>You can choose from the following options:</p>

                                    <ul class="list">
                                        <li><strong>“Heterosexual or Straight”</strong> –  means that a person is attracted to people of the opposite sex or gender</li>
                                        <li><strong>“Gay or Lesbian”</strong> –  means that a person is attracted to people of the same sex or gender</li>
                                        <li><strong>“Bisexual”</strong> –  means that a person is attracted to more than one sex or gender</li>
                                        <li><strong>“Other sexual orientation”</strong> –  enter your answer, for example, pansexual or asexual</li>
                                    </ul>

                                    <p>Attraction could be emotional, romantic or sexual.</p>

